aws_elastic_beanstalk_application_versio.description: Provides an Elastic Beanstalk Application Version Resource

name.description: A unique name for the this Application Version.

application.description: Name of the Beanstalk Application the version is associated with.

description.description: Short description of the Application Version.

bucket.description: S3 bucket that contains the Application Version source bundle.

key.description: S3 object that is the Application Version source bundle.

force_delete.description: On delete, force an Application Version to be deleted when it may be in use

arn.description: The ARN assigned by AWS for this Elastic Beanstalk Application.
